# StockAnalysis Project

## Project Overview
This is a stock analysis website that hosts AI-generated HTML analysis reports for US stocks. The site has a main landing page (`index.html`) that lists and links to individual stock reports.

## GitHub Repository
- URL: https://github.com/charithadc/StockAnalysis
- Remote: `origin` → `https://github.com/charithadc/StockAnalysis`

## Project Structure
```
index.html              ← main landing page listing all stock reports
reports/
  FERG/
  FIX/
  LPLA/
  LRCX/
  MSFT/
  VISA/
```
Each stock ticker has its own subfolder under `reports/` containing one or more HTML analysis report files.

## Conventions
- Report files are named `{TICKER}_Analysis_Report.html` or `{TICKER}_Analysis_Report_V2.html`
- Each new stock gets its own subfolder: `reports/{TICKER}/`
- The `index.html` must be updated whenever a new report is added so it shows up on the landing page

## Key Notes
- This is a Windows machine running PowerShell — use `;` instead of `&&` to chain shell commands
- The project uses plain HTML/CSS (no build tools or frameworks)
- Reports are standalone HTML files with embedded styles and scripts
